Flags Repository — Licensing
=============================

This repository contains three distinct layers, each under its own license.
Please respect all three.


1. Metadata and the database as a whole — CC BY-SA 4.0
------------------------------------------------------

The per-flag metadata (the `data/*.json` files), the aggregated index
(`data/flags.json`), and the structured collection as a whole — including the
schema, the curation, and the descriptive text — are licensed under the

    Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-SA 4.0)

    Copyright (c) 2026 Fredrik Niemelä

You are free to share and adapt this material for any purpose, including
commercially, provided that you give appropriate credit and distribute any
derivative database under the same license. Full legal text:

    https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/legalcode
    Summary: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

Some descriptive and historical prose is derived from Wikipedia and other
CC BY-SA sources; ShareAlike is chosen partly to keep that compatible.


